  <section class="mt25">
  <h3 class="center">Have any questions?</h3>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span6">
      <h4>Q:Which credit cards are accepted?</h4>
      <p>A:We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, JCB, Discover, and Diners Club.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <h4>Q:Any hidden fees?</h4>
      <p>A:Absolutely not. There are no setup, cancelation, support, usage, or any other fees.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span6">
      <h4>Q:Is my payment information secure?</h4>
      <p>A:Our website is fully PCI compliant, and uses the same encryption that banks use. View our article about security practices to learn more: <%= link_to "How does Zarlu keep my data safe?", "/blog/how-does-zarlu-keep-my-data-safe", target: "_blank" %>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <h4>Q:Do you have a money back guarentee?</h4>
      <p>A:If you are not thrilled with Zarlu, we do not want your money. We will refund any payment made within the last thirty days if you are unsatisfied for any reason.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span6">
      <h4>Q:Does the free plan really have no time limit?</h4>
      <p>A:No catch! The free plan has no time or usage limits. We are confident that you will love our software and we want to give you the opportunity to try it for as long as you like. No pressure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <h4>Q:Does Zarlu offer enterprise plans?</h4>
      <p>A:We have Enterprise plans availble for customers with more than 150 staffers. Click on the 'Contact Us' link above and send us a message to learn more.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span6">
      <h4>Q:Unanswered questions?</h4>
      <p>A:Click on the above 'Contact Us' link to send any unanswered questions. We are happy to answer any questions you have!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <h4>Q:Do you have customer support?</h4>
      <p>A:Our engineers do their best to answer all support requests within 24 hours. Click on the 'Contact Us' link to contact our engineers directly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</div>
